column1: Daily Weather Observations for Taree, New South Wales for August 2021
Prepared at 16:00 UTC on Saturday 16 October 2021   IDCJDW2129.202108
Observations from Taree Airport, about 6 km from the centre of Taree.
Some cloud observations are from automated equipment; these are somewhat different to those made by a human observer and may not appear every day.
Observations were drawn from Taree Airport AWS {station 060141}
